Dave Brockie, 50, was found dead on March 23, 2014, at his Richmond, Virginia home . 
 Medical examiner ruled Brockie died of accidental acute heroin toxicity . 
 His father, William Brockie filed lawsuit against band seeking $1million in compensatory damages on top of unspecified punitive damages . 
 Suit alleges bandmates stole his remains, guitars, artwork and a gold record . 
 When Mr Brockie demanded to have his son's ashes back, GWAR members allegedly gave him a small portion in a used plastic bag . 
 